messages.messageBody:
I don't know Brenda, 6 or 7 people? <g>
Kelli
Alan & Brenda Leonard <abtleo@...> wrote:11/1/02 18:50:

> All I have to say to my dh is "Europe"and he would be all over it.
> We've said we want to go back over there and May would be a good time,

Hmmm. So how many should I be booking for the very fancy guestroom at Chez
Leonard? <g>

I'm just a quick train ride north of Frankfurt!

I discovered today that my new apartment comes with a maid's room in the
basement. Now, why they thought someone in one of these dinky places would
need a maid, I don't know. But it might make a decent guest room when
cleaned. I think it was probably last cleaned by the outgoing maid...about
50 years ago or so! Ugh!

brenda

messages.msgSnippet: In Vermont we have to send in 3-6 examples of schooling for each subject by law each year. It is hard to unschool because I have to watch what they are doing
messages.messageBody:
In Vermont we have to send in 3-6 examples of "schooling" for each
subject by law each year. It is hard to unschool because I have to watch
what they are doing - make it fit the subject matter that the state has
put together, etc. How can I get around that? Michele
